<br />
Shadow: there is really no strategy here. but the strategy is to get out as many minions ap possible and use the sneaks to help set up for a late game swarm. saruman is there for condition removal. </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
